HEADWORD: Spitz dog
<hw>Spitz" dog"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[G. <ets>spitz</ets>,
<ets>spitzhund</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A breed of dogs
having erect ears and long silky hair, usually white; -- called also
<altname>Pomeranian dog</altname>, and
<altname>louploup</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

